Node.Notes: Assumes: [they are] to you a gift, ones dedicated to Yahweh, to do the work of the Tent of Meeting.
Uncertain. P-PP-S-PP assumes forward pointing this (starting in v. 12): This [is] what is set aside of their gifts for you in relation to all the wave offerings of the sons of Israel.
Uncertain. Assumes: You must redeem its redemption price from a month old at your price with five shekels of silver according to the shekel of the sanctuary.
Assumes: which [tithe] they present to Yahweh as an offering.
